Class FollowRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301f17t13.com.catisadog.models.followrequest.FollowRequest

  • public class FollowRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    A FollowRequest. Represents a relationship between two users, where one user has made a follow request to another user. If the followee has accepted the follower request, accepted is true.
